data.description: Back on the market through no fault of the home! Big doesn't begin to describe it! If you're in the market for a spacious home then look no further. This sprawling corner-lot retreat goes on forever with over 3400+ square feet, 3 living areas, double ovens, an office nook, and 3.5 baths. Resplendent with brand-new carpet, the home features a fresh interior paint job. Every room in this home is gigantic, including each of the five bedrooms and the walk-in closets! If it's storage you crave then you'll love the walk-in pantry and laundry room. Rounding out the high points is an ample backyard and covered patio for when you want to enjoy those endless summer nights.
